  "3268510": {
    "name": "Hotel Luximinal",
    "steam_appid": 3268510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款神秘的解谜游戏，挑战你的心智，把你拖入一场深邃的时空冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Hotel Luximinal 里，有些事情并不正常。房间在移动，物品在变化，电梯正在考验你的耐心与理智。你被指派调查这家酒店中发生的异常事件 —— 并记录下你发现的每一个异常。但你在酒店里停留得越久，深入得越深，你就越有可能失去理智。现在，就是你解开谜团的时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/732fc3d65c42e28a3c31f2b24ed44ceb.avif?t=1765918901\" width=486 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f3a7aecc2960e1e7fb378c65324335d9.poster.avif?t=1765918901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f3a7aecc2960e1e7fb378c65324335d9.webm?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f3a7aecc2960e1e7fb378c65324335d9.mp4?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>7 个充满神秘魅力的关卡</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Golden Suites</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Private Poolroom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hotel Gallery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waiting Area</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handsome Bar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elegant Office</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting Suite</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/07639c19f1a686c4ad8a56270a36a866.avif?t=1765918901\" width=486 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/2a35ac9ce557b67e640c5add6be3ccad.poster.avif?t=1765918901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/2a35ac9ce557b67e640c5add6be3ccad.webm?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/2a35ac9ce557b67e640c5add6be3ccad.mp4?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你将体验到</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异常侦探</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有你和你敏锐的眼睛：会移动的画作、位置改变的家具、乍看之下不可见的线索。每一次发现都让你更接近真相 —— 也更深入酒店的深处。做出正确的推理。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纯粹的疯狂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你以为自己明白了 —— 但酒店却嘲笑你的自信。它玩弄你的心智，测试你的耐心，挑战你的毅力。你能在不放弃、不作弊的情况下完成考验吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的时间线挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优雅的房间，充满寂静与试炼 —— 熟悉，却又来自不属于此刻的年代。一家本身就像谜题般存在的酒店。每一个关卡、每一张图像、几乎每一个异常都想告诉你一些什么 —— 如果你愿意仔细观察，并将线索串联起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f416ea14625c0bf3f83d1e7428184cde.avif?t=1765918901\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找出全部 210 个异常！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡有 30 个异常</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些容易发现</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些较为棘手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花时间记住每个细节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进度，关卡难度逐渐增加</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心，否则你可能永远被困！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/a965a14a2b8c9f390590e6464ef72ced.avif?t=1765918901\" width=486 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/9faa5e9e0258d7b16f98bd05a97b36e5.poster.avif?t=1765918901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/9faa5e9e0258d7b16f98bd05a97b36e5.webm?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/9faa5e9e0258d7b16f98bd05a97b36e5.mp4?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次正确选择，你将上升一层。连续正确 7 次即可返回大堂。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则很简单：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从第 0 层开始</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入房间时：记住房间的每一个细节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你认为没有异常：进入“另一个”电梯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你认为有异常：返回起始电梯</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果判断正确：上升一层</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果判断错误：重新从第 0 层开始</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要连续正确 8 次</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后解锁下一个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为公司成功的研究员离开酒店</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f0702431cc8c0ddacaad1ad9a4a66d63.avif?t=1765918901\" width=486 height=77 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/af4cbb822eb85331b8cd61faf807f2bd.avif?t=1765918901\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>为什么 Hotel Luximinal 与众不同</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>侦探工作与异常狩猎：</strong> 你找到的异常越多，拼图就越完整。当你征服所有关卡后，便能最终解开酒店的谜团。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重复游玩：</strong> 解锁所有关卡后，异常会重置并随机出现在新位置。再次挑战自己 —— 你还能记得它们吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越三个魅力时代的时光旅行：</strong> 1925、2025、2125 —— 从 Art Deco 的黄金年代到 Luximinal 的未来幻想，仿生人和时光机的交织愿景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心智挑战：</strong> 对于不满足于短暂异常狩猎的玩家 —— 一系列相互关联的谜题正等着你。你能多快解开所有谜团？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>七个关卡，七夜疯狂：</strong> 一周的诡异娱乐。每晚挑战一个关卡 —— 然后恢复理智，如果你能的话。不久之后，你将比熟悉自己的房间更了解这家酒店。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式 Art Deco 设计：</strong> 优雅与不安的超现实混合，灵感来自 1920 年代的华丽风格，并带有梦幻色彩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘氛围：</strong> 动态音景、令人不安的视觉效果和史诗般的音乐 —— 在酒店大堂中特别震撼。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/b402dd536fa37bd7f7366ffa845e8cb7.poster.avif?t=1765918901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/b402dd536fa37bd7f7366ffa845e8cb7.webm?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/b402dd536fa37bd7f7366ffa845e8cb7.mp4?t=1765918901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >认识 Payton</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是 <strong>Payton</strong> —— 礼宾、安保仿生人，以及帝国的忠诚助理。我引导宾客穿越酒店闪耀的长廊，帮助他们发现秘密，并维持秩序 —— 即使连时间本身似乎已经破碎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外表优雅、职责精准，却与 Luximinal 的奇异命运紧密相连。当你在酒店中徘徊时，我会注视着你。我在此是为了服务 —— 但也是为了挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268510/extras/f2c0bec44c956944e7505fbd3b60aedf.avif?t=1765918901\" width=616 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奖励：</strong> 在大厅里，你会找到一台自动点唱机播放音乐。享受旋律，点击切换曲目，让氛围包围你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jazz</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >柔和的背景音乐</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这家酒店正在呼唤你 —— 并将考验你。你会找到所有的异常，还是会被它们永远困在酒店里？</p>",
